(Overview) Tj
T*
(Atomic structure explains how protons, neutrons, and electrons make up atoms.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Atomic Structure in Chemistry using accurate subject) Tj
T*
(vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind particle arrangement and how atomic number defines an) Tj
T*
(element.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Atomic Structure to examples such as describing the structure of sodium or) Tj
T*
(oxygen.) Tj
T*
(- Avoid common errors and build confidence through counting subatomic particles.) Tj
T*
() Tj
